{"tid":1784490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗國民仲記唔記得722市面？","createTime":"2019-12-15T16:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T17:41:34.000Z","uid":263198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9fdc5228eb55e2f46459bc075260dec95cb077","tid":1784490,"uid":263198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"小弟都係元朗國民<br />\n當日睇住大馬路堆鋪頭由中午開始就逐間落閘<br />\n我番個間公司都比平日早幾個鐘收工<br />\n<br />\n當然今時今日流浮山200刀手應該仲做緊準備<br />\n不過好記得個時電話group收到唔少錄音<br />\n仲實牙實齒話722一定見後生就斬<br />\n要幫某某老婆報仇之類<br />\n<br />\n我係度諗、好彩個日只係平常日子姐<br />\n如果大時大節搞D咁既留言出來<br />\n影響到D商家無得開鋪、市民無得食大餐既話就真係陰功豬啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V8KG21e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8KG21e.jpg&h=a4c83d68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzgNYzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzgNYzC.jpg&h=55b6b8f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ade9207c90acfdab4c4cdee802315488dd41b6e6","tid":1784490,"uid":262914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"聽完段錄音真係嚇到瀬屎<br />\n<br />\n聖誕假期千其千其唔好再流出呀，唔係零售真係冚家剷架啦"},{"pid":"61545a01b956d7d33fcdf862a51288b321a466f7","tid":1784490,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"sorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>手足無證無據都生豬肉坐咗半年<br />\n又話手足唔係condom？<br />\n就快生豬肉到2020年<br />\n可唔可以幫手關注下呢單野<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGaZPt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGaZPt9.jpg&h=6915346d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}